FBIS3-15597 "drsov045_d_94003" FBIS-SOV-94-045 Document Type:Daily Report 8 Mar 1994 Regional Affairs Yeltsin Releases Representative in Tambov PM0703151394 Moscow ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA in Russian 5 Mar 94 First Edition p 1 PM0703151394 Moscow ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Unattributed "Official Report"] [Text] By edict of the Russian Federation president, Valentin Vladimirovich Davituliani has been released from the post of the Russian Federation president's representative in Tambov Oblast at his own request (Article 31 of the Russian Federation Labor Law Code). By decree of the Russian Federation Federal Assembly Federation Council, Vladimir Apollonovich Nikitov is confirmed as leader of the Federation Council apparatus.
